%h3
  Install jRuby (default version is 1.3.1), but do not use it right now.
%pre.code
  :preserve
    ∴  rvm install jruby
%h3
  Use Ruby 1.9.1, installs if necessary
%pre.code
  :preserve
    ∴  rvm use ruby -v 1.9.1
%h3
  Equivalent to "rvm use ruby -v 1.9.1", due to defaults
%pre.code
  :preserve
    ∴  rvm 1.9.1
